{"tid":182433,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(DSE GEOG)地理地理 健心做起","createTime":"2017-04-01T10:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T13:34:34.000Z","uid":72795,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"54787658be3bf23eab8cac6be1819ed072757058","tid":182433,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T10:45:57.000Z","msg":"所謂&rdquo;心態決定境界&rdquo;, 你想5*,首先要有一顆可以容納5*的心。<br />\n<br />\n考試唔單單係測試學生的知識，其實同樣重要的是考試技巧+表達能力。<br />\n<br />\n好多學生問我：我死溫十日可唔可以5*？<br />\n<br />\n我可以講，你講得出呢句，代表你未有考試的心，未有考試技巧。<br />\n<br />\n你點樣死溫呢？ 用幾耐死溫呢？ 用咩形式死溫呢？ 點解死溫完都無信心呢？<br />\n<br />\n重點係你有幾準確去溫，每一次溫書可以幫到你幾多，可以回答到邊類型的問題。<br />\n<br />\n所以你要想高分，先要放下GEOG可以&rdquo;死溫&rdquo;呢個諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想搵CE + AL GEOG 皆A 的GEOG 考試技巧將軍，歡迎 telegram<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"http://t.me/Scottish_Salmon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FScottish_Salmon&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSergdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=b38116e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/Scottish_Salmon</a>"},{"pid":"58687bd4cad24ad70a8da4b514d54f62a3b4250c","tid":182433,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T10:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b347c1f62ecb86e6633946b0e6453130e271c74","tid":182433,"uid":94568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T10:48:18.000Z","msg":"主科都未考 咁快溫定地理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f2837310d193eab3ac468d374312158c326ea8","tid":182433,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T10:53:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>主科都未考 咁快溫定地理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個係一個都市傳說<br />\n<br />\n其實地理同主科關係密切，由你點樣組織文章、用字，到增加文章內容，地理同主科係相輔相成。<br />\n<br />\n5*潛能可以令你同時進步，概念技巧互相運用，但係普遍的學生只會單程學習，咁樣所以你花五個鐘只能進步一科，優秀學生可以五個鐘同時進步兩科 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b4c02f2cf7af2a1a2e115965f565426c044645a","tid":182433,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T10:54:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e011195284ecc63949fd7e333ee50784d4b945b7","tid":182433,"uid":68913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T10:55:27.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"5b058abca9aa2c87ad446c2f52ee00ccc466c590","tid":182433,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T10:58:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名</blockquote><br />\n背 寫 諗 掙扎！！！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85333217e50108f39c9ac8dd95b52aca33f7298","tid":182433,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T11:00:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51cdc0bd26c65900be93483c5be084c97d146f29","tid":182433,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T11:02:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3c19c037b7b3d34ad8ecfa60a02bec90b38dc3a3","tid":182433,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T11:02:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"18aa67c12cc7a64e7d3772e59e44cdf28efda06a","tid":182433,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T11:03:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"47ce02c49ebc0ebabc934b858cde5bde3d4c0eea","tid":182433,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T11:31:58.000Z","msg":"<i